|---|---|
| **Security headers** | Add `helmet` to set protective HTTP headers automatically |
| **Rate limiting** | Add `express-rate-limit` to prevent brute-force/DoS |
| **Body size limit** | `express.json({ limit: '10kb' })` prevents payload attacks |
| **Input validation** | Validate and sanitize query params before use |
| **Error propagation** | Use `next(err)` in routes to centralize error handling |
| **Error responses** | Sanitize error messages in production; log details server-side only |
| **404 handling** | Explicit 404 middleware instead of silent no-response |
| **Port config** | Read `PORT` from environment instead of hardcoding |
| **Module export** | Export both `app` and `server` to allow clean shutdown in tests |

